    "body": "Sorry to bother you, I also encountered the same problem. I tried setting LC_XXX, but it didn't seem to work. May I ask how you solved it?\r\n\r\nI am using wsl 2.1.3.0 , zsh  5.9 (x86_64-pc-linux-gnu)， and startship 1.18.2\r\nthis is my locale\r\n\r\n❯ cat /etc/default/locale\r\nLC_CTYPE=en_US.UTF-8\r\nLC_ALL=en_US.UTF-8\r\nLANG=en_US.UTF-8",
